snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance II Saints and Sinners Trailer
snippet.description:
Share in the adventures of Henry as you explore the beautiful but unforgiving world of Kingdom Come: Deliverance II, a thrilling Action RPG set amid the chaos of a civil war in 15th Century Bohemia.

Righteousness or vice: what path will you take? Will you try and save the world or punish it for its sins? Your actions shape Henry and the world around him in this ultimate open-world adventure.

Kingdom Come: Deliverance II arrives on PC, Xbox Series X|S, and PlayStation 5 on February 4, 2025.

Pre-order now: https://bit.ly/PreorderKCD2

X/Twitter: https://x.com/KingdomComeRPG
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kingdomcomerpg
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kingdomcomerpg/
